trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref href="System.Type"></xref> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty"></xref> class that has the specified property name.
The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Type> property of a print system object, including casing.
The name of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty"></xref> represents.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty"></xref> class that has the specified property name and value.
The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Type> property of a print system object, including casing.
The name of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty"></xref> represents.
The value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty"></xref> represents.
Gets or sets the value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty"></xref> represents.
The value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty"></xref> represents.
